Rhinox/Sniper


Rhinox sees all the missles and bullets coming towards him, He
quickly 
thought to himself,'how stupid was I to run straight.' He turned in 
ran to the left, having most of the bullet miss him, he had some hit. 
He didn't flinch, but kept running. He had to get into the base. He 
then turns to the right and starts to run into zig-zag.

Sniper grabs his com link. "Iron Raptor, Get your ass out here and 
bring prowl or who ever you can get out here too, We are under attack 
and only 2 or 3 can continue fight the rest need cr chambers, fast." 
Sniper tokk out his rocket launcher and set his rifle to rapid fire. 
he fired 20 shoots form his rifle at anubis. He fires to rockets at 
sixshot. Sniper looked up and saw Rain clouds, "That will make it a 
little darker so it might help."
